comments: Jackson (DET) makes marginal contact with his forearm to Barton's (DEN) side during his drive toward the lane.
Doumbouya (DET) briefly places his arms around Grant's (DEN) upper half before correcting. Doumbouya (DET) then makes clean contact with the ball as the entry pass is made.
Doumbouya (DET) moves laterally into Morris' (DEN) path and initiates contact to his side during his drive along the baseline.
Brown (DET) makes marginal contact with Barton's (DEN) backside as he drives inside the perimeter.
Brown (DET) makes contact with Barton's (DEN) wrist during his upward shooting motion.
Barton (DEN) and Jackson (DET) engage and disengage off-ball.
Jokic (DEN) makes simultaneous contact with the ball and Jackson's (DET) arm during his driving shot.
Drummond (DET) makes marginal contact with Jokic's (DEN) backside during his drive into the lane.
Brown (DET) makes marginal contact with Barton's (DEN) side during rebounding.
Drummond (DET) and Jokic (DEN) briefly engage and disengage in the lane.
Jokic (DEN) makes marginal contact with Jackson's (DET) body after he has gathered the ball and pivots to pass in the lane.
Jokic (DEN) moves laterally into Jackson's (DET) path and turns into his side after his gather, creating contact that affects Jackson's driving shot attempt.
Drummond (DET) momentarily places a hand to Jokic's (DEN) front as they disengage from the screen on the perimeter.
Jokic (DEN) establishes himself in a legal screening position in Brown's (DET) path firms up on his left leg creating marginal contact as they disengage from the pick.
Mykhailiuk (DET) engages and disengages with Barton (DEN) during the inbound.
Jokic (DEN) commits a take foul on Jackson (DET).
Craig (DEN) briefly places his arms around Drummond's (DET) midsection before correcting.
Drummond (DET) turns slightly into Craig (DEN) following the hand off and makes some marginal contact.
Grant (DEN) makes incidental contact with Brown's (DET) left arm after initially making clean contact with the ball.
Maker (DET) establishes himself in a legal screening position in Barton's (DEN) path and does not deliver the contact.
Barton (DEN) plants his left foot to the floor prior to making incidental foot contact with the ball thereafter.
Barton (DEN) extends his hands forward and initiates contact with Jackson's (DET) front.
Maker (DET) makes marginal contact with Jokic's (DEN) back and side as he drives into the lane.
Brown (DET) makes contact to Jokic's (DEN) left arm during his upward shooting motion.
Jackson (DET) briefly places his arms around Brown's (DET) upper half during the inbound before correcting.
Barton (DEN) makes marginal contact with Jackson's (DET) left arm after crossing half-court.
Jokic (DEN) and Maker (DET) engage and disengage off-ball.
Jackson (DET) does not initiate contact to Barton's (DEN) side or front as Barton trips over Jokic's (DEN) foot, causing him to lose balance.
Grant (DEN) moves laterally into Snell's (DET) path and fails to establish legal guarding position prior to body contact occurring along the sideline.
Jackson (DET) and Morris (DEN) engage and disengage off-ball.
Maker (DET) makes marginal contact with Jokic's (DEN) back and side as Jokic (DEN) backs Maker (DET) down in the post.

Snell (DET) makes marginal contact with Grant's (DEN) head as he simultaneously makes contact with the ball during Grant's upward shooting motion. Contact to an opponents head/face can be deemed marginal when the result of a natural basketball move, provided the contact is not disproportionate or uncontrolled.
Morris (DEN) commits a take foul on Brown (DET).
Barton (DEN) and Brown (DET) engage and disengage during the inbound.
Brown (DET) makes incidental contact to the arm of Jokic (DEN) after the release of his jump shot.
Jackson (DET) and Barton (DEN) engage and disengage off-ball.
Maker (DET) makes marginal contact with Barton's (DEN) side after the release of the jump shot attempt.
Jackson (DET) cleanly dislodges the pass intended for Barton's (DEN).
